# Feature modules

Mirror `src/modules/categories/` and `src/modules/products/`.

- Class names: `ProductsService`, not `ProductService`
- Inject other features via their module `exports`, not by reaching into Prisma of another domain when a service method exists
- `update` / `remove`: `await this.findOne(id)` then mutate
- DTOs: `dto/index.ts` re-exports create, update, response
- Return types: prefer `*ResponseDto` (or Prisma model on create if already used in that module)

When scaffolding a new module, use the **create-nest-module** skill.
